page.title: 05Norton & Lenchwick People
page.content: On the 8.7.85. 2 Children did these activities: Ian Wild.Got up at 08.00 and had Shreddies for breakfast.For lunch he had sandwiches and cake.For tea he had Potatoes,Cabbage,Meat,Gravy,Raspberry Angel Delight and Ice Cream.He Watched Childrens I.T.V.and Listened to Radio Wyvern.He read Pippen Comic.He bought a newspaper,\lb of wine gums and 6 packets of plain crisps.He played with Richard Jonson and Chris Hodgekins. Chris Hodgkins.Got up at 08.00 and had a drink of milk for his breakfast. For dinner he had sandwiches, Blackberry Sundae.For tea he had chips,bacon and beans and to drink Lemon and Lime.He listened to Pop songs on Radio 1.He bought crisps and played with Ian Wild and Chris Print.
